item.title: By: Spencer Haley
item.dc:creator: Spencer Haley
item.description: Dude - my all time favorite books are A Brave New World, 1984, and anything by Ayn Rand! I also liked the matrix and V for Vendetta! Ayn Rand's Atlas Shrugged Part 1 was just made into a movie, did you see it? So awesome!
item.content:encoded: Dude – my all time favorite books are A Brave New World, 1984, and anything by Ayn Rand! I also liked the matrix and V for Vendetta! Ayn Rand’s Atlas Shrugged Part 1 was just made into a movie, did you see it? So awesome!
